videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown finds WR Kobay White on the screen and he takes it all the way for a 76-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Brown connects with White for big TD

videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown completes a 46-yard pass to WR Michael Walker for a big gain.
videos.headline: Boston College capitalizes on flea flicker for big gain

videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown finds TE Tommy Sweeney in the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Brown extends BC lead with 2nd passing TD

videos.description: Virginia QB Kurt Benkert is pressured and decides to casually flip the ball down the field leading to an easy interception.
videos.headline: Benkert tosses questionable pass for 1st INT

videos.description: Virginia WR Joe Reed muscles his way up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Reed leaps through defense for TD

videos.description: Boston College RB Jon Hilliman takes the toss to the outside for a 29-yard gain.
videos.headline: Hilliman shakes off defenders on big run

videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown finds TE Tommy Sweeney over in the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown, his second on the day.
videos.headline: Brown connects with Sweeney for 2nd TD

videos.description: Backup Virginia QB Lindell Stone throws a pick-six on his second pass attempt of the game to extend the Boston College lead.
videos.headline: Lamont picks off Stone for TD

videos.description: Backup Virginia QB Lindell Stone is intercepted by DB Hamp Cheevers for his second interception of the game.
videos.headline: Stone throws 2nd INT of quarter
